# * Lot syntax

# ** 1. Ledger-style lot syntax is parsed and reproduced in print output.
<
2026-01-01
    assets:investment    10 AAPL @ $100 {$100} [2026-01-01] (lot A)
    assets:cash

$ hledger -f- print
2026-01-01
    assets:investment    10 AAPL {$100} [2026-01-01] (lot A) @ $100
    assets:cash

>=

